                                <item>
                                                            <title><![CDATA[ 6 exquisite homes with vast acreage ]]></title>
                                                                                                                                                                                                <link>https://theweek.com/culture-life/property/6-exquisite-homes-vast-acreage</link>
                                                                            <description>
                            <![CDATA[ Featuring an off-the-grid contemporary home in New Mexico and lakefront farmhouse in Massachusetts ]]>
                                                                                                            </description>
